'''沿海捲心菜'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Lepidium oleraceum''}}）<ref name=Laws2014>{{cite book |page=49 |chapter=甜橘 |title=改變歷史的50種植物|author=[[比爾·勞斯|比爾·勞斯]]（{{lang|en|Bill Laws}}），[[王建鎧|王建鎧]]譯 |editor1=[[王秀婷_(台灣)|王秀婷]] |editor2=[[魏嘉儀|魏嘉儀]] |publisher=積木文化 |location=臺北市 |edition=初版 |date=2014-01-08 |language=zh-hant |isbn=978-986-5865-35-1 }}</ref>为[[十字花科|十字花科]][[独行菜属|独行菜属]]的[[草本植物|草本植物]]，[[原生物種|原生]]於[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]，是紐西蘭的[[特有種|特有種]]。<ref name="New Zealand Flora">{{cite web |url=http://nzflora.landcareresearch.co.nz/default.aspx?NameID=Landcareresearch.co.nz/PS1/NK/225615 |title=New Zealand Flora |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165459/http://nzflora.landcareresearch.co.nz/default.aspx?NameID=Landcareresearch.co.nz%2FPS1%2FNK%2F225615 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Lepidium oleraceum. Nau. Cook's scurvy grass. |url=http://maoriplantuse.landcareresearch.co.nz/WebForms/PeoplePlantsDetails.aspx?firstcome=firstcome&PKey=C07F5A45-8273-4346-B9A1-F005092C3BEF |publisher=Landcare research |accessdate=2012-04-02 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192911/http://maoriplantuse.landcareresearch.co.nz/WebForms/PeoplePlantsDetails.aspx?firstcome=firstcome&PKey=C07F5A45-8273-4346-B9A1-F005092C3BEF |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==變種==
本物種現時有三個已知的變種<ref name="Flora of New Zealand: Taxa"/>：
*''Lepidium oleraceum'' var. ''frondosum'' Kirk 
*''Lepidium oleraceum'' var. ''acutidentatum'' Kirk
*''Lepidium oleraceum'' var. ''serrulatum'' Thell.

==分佈==
在紐西蘭，本物種原生於各處的海岸，包括有：[[北島_(紐西蘭)|北島]]、[[南島_(新西蘭)|南島]]、
[[斯圖爾特島|斯圖爾特島]]、[[三王群岛|三王群岛]]、[[斯奈尔斯群岛|斯奈尔斯群岛]]、[[查塔姆群岛|查塔姆群岛]]、[[奥克兰群岛|奥克兰群岛]]、[[安蒂波德斯群岛|安蒂波德斯群岛]]及[[邦蒂群岛|邦蒂群岛]]<ref name="Flora of New Zealand: Taxa">{{cite web |url=http://floraseries.landcareresearch.co.nz/pages/Taxon.aspx?id=_265b6c83-9bf3-41e2-af86-fe8a4c971a5f&fileName=Flora%201.xml |title=Flora of New Zealand: Taxa |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2008-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022034247/http://floraseries.landcareresearch.co.nz/pages/Taxon.aspx?id=_265b6c83-9bf3-41e2-af86-fe8a4c971a5f&fileName=Flora%201.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Amey et al.">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsnz.org/publish/nzjb/2007/006.php |title=Amey et al.—Lepidium oleraceum on Bounty Islands |accessdate=2007-04-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706145945/http://www.rsnz.org/publish/nzjb/2007/006.php |archivedate=2008-07-06 |language=en }}</ref>。
雖然當歐洲人初來紐西蘭時，本物種大量曾經到處都是<ref name=Laws2014 /><ref name=":0" /><ref>Cooper & Cambie 1991</ref>，但現時主要都只在離岸的石堆或{{link-en|洲渚|islet}}之上<ref name="Landcare Research"/>。

==保育狀況==
現時本物種的數量很少，屬於高危類別。當中一個原因是這些物種依賴數量在減少中的[[海鳥|海鳥]]，當牠們築巢時，為泥土帶來的高度營養。另外，本物種亦會被多㮔動物食用，例如：[[牲畜|牲畜]]、[[嚙齒類|嚙齒類]]、[[蝸牛|蝸牛]]及[[食草动物|素食類]][[昆蟲|昆蟲]]諸如[[小菜蛾|小菜蛾]]、[[菜粉蝶|菜粉蝶]]等<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal |url=http://newzealandecology.org/nzje/2966 |title=White butterfly (Pieris rapae) and the white rust Albugo candida on Cook’s scurvy grass (Lepidium oleraceum) |last1=Hasenbank |first1=M. |last2=Brandon |first2=M. |last3=Hartley |first3=S. |year=2011 |journal=New Zealand Journal of Ecology |volume=35 |pages=69-75 |access-date=2016-06-07 |language=en |archive-date=2016-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923165352/http://newzealandecology.org/nzje/2966 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。植株也會感染白銹病（white rust），白銹病是由[[卵菌綱|卵菌綱]]的[[病原菌|病原菌]]白銹菌（''Albugo candida''）所造成的。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="Landcare Research">{{cite web|title=Conservation genetics of threatened plants|url=http://www.landcareresearch.co.nz/research/biocons/genetics/projects/plant_conservation.asp|publisher=Landcare Research|accessdate=2008-04-29|archive-date=2010-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100517154037/http://landcareresearch.co.nz/research/biocons/genetics/projects/plant_conservation.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==食用==
本物種的嫩葉可生吃或煮熟來吃。含有豐富的[[維生素C|維生素C]]，早從大航海時代就已經是重要的維生素C來源，令航海者免於患上[[壞血病|壞血病]]<ref name=Laws2014 /><ref name="Plants For A Future">{{cite web |url=http://www.pfaf.org/database/plants.php?Lepidium+oleraceum |title=Lepidium oleraceum - Plants For A Future database report |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184212/http://www.pfaf.org/database/plants.php?Lepidium+oleraceum |dead-url=no }}</ref>。葉子的味道與[[水芹_(十字花科)|水芹]]相似<ref name="Plants For A Future" />。

